    Verse(id: 'v522', text: 'Make every effort to keep the unity of the Spirit through the bond of peace.', reference: 'Ephesians 4:3', book: 'Ephesians', chapter: 4, verseNumber: 3, topics: ['peace', 'love', 'bible-verses']),
